mathematica: terms = 40; f[q_] = LatticeData["A6", "ThetaSeriesFunction"][-I Log[q]/Pi]; s = Series[f[q], {q, 0, 2 terms}]; DeleteCases[CoefficientList[s, q^(1/2) ] // Round, 0][[1 ;; terms]] (* _Jean-François Alcover_, Jul 04 2017 *)
